WEBVTT

00:00:00.921 --> 00:00:04.174
You know, my friends,
I look at this photograph

00:00:04.198 --> 00:00:06.643
and I have to ask myself,

00:00:06.667 --> 00:00:09.277
you know, I think I've seen this
somewhere before.

00:00:09.657 --> 00:00:12.457
People marching in the street for justice.

00:00:12.903 --> 00:00:16.354
But I know it's not the same photograph
that I would have seen,

00:00:16.378 --> 00:00:20.845
because I wouldn't take my oath
to be a police officer until 1989.

00:00:21.315 --> 00:00:24.649
And I've been in the business
for over 25 years.

00:00:24.673 --> 00:00:27.045
And identifying
as an African-American woman,

00:00:27.069 --> 00:00:29.244
I know things have gotten better.

